---
// No props needed - this is a static section
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background gradient for depth -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 opacity-50"></div>

  <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Main headline with impact -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-display mb-4">
          We Get It. SEO Has a Bad Wrap...
        </h2>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-8">
          And It's Deserved.
        </p>

        <!-- Truth paragraph -->
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          After 10 years in this industry, we've seen it all. Agencies charging thousands for
          'SEO packages' that are just automated reports. Consultants who disappear after the
          contract is signed. Empty promises of 'page 1 rankings' with no actual results.
          <span class="block mt-4 text-white font-semibold">
            The truth? 90% of SEO agencies are selling snake oil.
          </span>
          <span class="block mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-primary-400">
            We're part of the 10% who actually deliverâ€”with transparent reporting, real rankings, and measurable ROI.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Proof points grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Proof Point 1 -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-2">See Live Rankings</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Within 30 days or your money back. No excuses, just results.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Proof Point 2 -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-2">Full Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Know exactly what we're doing, when, and why. No black box BS.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Proof Point 3 -->
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-2">Pay for Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Month-to-month. Stay because of results, not contracts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Strong CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent-500 text-gray-900 font-bold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-400 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl"
        >
          See Our Track Record
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
          No BS. No contracts. Just results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Subtle pattern overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"%3E%3Cg fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"%3E%3Cg fill="%239C92AC" fill-opacity="0.4"%3E%3Cpath d="M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Add custom animations for impact */
  @keyframes slideInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  h2 {
    animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .text-accent-400 {
    animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  p {
    animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  .grid > div {
    animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
  }

  /* Enhanced hover effects */
  .group:hover h3 {
    color: rgb(60 139 218);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
</style>